{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "df973704-190b-466d-a503-d221f8f2b35c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/df973704-190b-466d-a503-d221f8f2b35c@1.pkg/1772597667224/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597667901", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/df973704-190b-466d-a503-d221f8f2b35c@1.pkg/1772597667224/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597667901"}, "identifier": "df973704-190b-466d-a503-d221f8f2b35c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查法治的作用。</p>\n\n<p>A:法治的作用涵盖立法、执法、司法、守法等多个环节，题干中执法行动体现法治的落实，但“最重要”这一表述缺乏依据，故A说法错误。</p>\n\n<p>B:市场监督管理局和公安部门依法查处违法企业，维护市场秩序，直接体现法治是市场经济健康发展的重要保障，故B符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>C:法律保障的是消费者的合法权益，而非“一切权益”，表述绝对化，故C说法错误。</p>\n\n<p>D:司法由司法机关(如法院、检察院)负责，而题干中的执法属于行政机关的行政行为，与司法无关，故D不符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）2025年央视“3·15”晚会曝光部分企业生产的一次性内裤号称“纯棉”“灭菌”，实际却在脏乱车间徒手生产、材质造假，且数量巨大，多渠道流入市场。事件曝光后，当地市场监督管理局联合公安部门迅速到达涉事企业现场，开展执法行动。这充分体现（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）2025年央视“3·15”晚会曝光部分企业生产的一次性内裤号称“纯棉”“灭菌”，实际却在脏乱车间徒手生产、材质造假，且数量巨大，多渠道流入市场。事件曝光后，当地市场监督管理局联合公安部门迅速到达涉事企业现场，开展执法行动。这充分体现（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/df973704-190b-466d-a503-d221f8f2b35c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755143570043", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>法治最重要的作用体现在执法环节</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>法治是发展市场经济的重要保障</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>我国法律保障消费者的一切权益</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>司法是捍卫公平正义的最后防线</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编）2025年央视“3·15”晚会曝光部分企业生产的一次性内裤号称“纯棉”“灭菌”，实际却在脏乱车间徒手生产、材质造假，且数量巨大，多渠道流入市场。事件曝光后，当地市场监督管理局联合公安部门迅速到达涉事企业现场，开展执法行动。这充分体现（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "df973704-190b-466d-a503-d221f8f2b35c", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）2025年央视“3·15”晚会曝光部分企业生产的一次性内裤号称“纯棉”“灭菌”，实际却在脏乱车间徒手生产、材质造假，且数量巨